reviews.review_text: Incredible I’m only just getting into this matrix, but I can already tell this is going to be incredible. The other sources of this show sound alright, but this matrix brings out the best in the sources used. It sounds very clear and open. The show itself is a great one too, especially with the jammy Let it Grow into Drums and the extended Wang Dang Doodle jam(Bob’s vocal mic wasn’t working I believe). This is great; thank you Hunter for all the great matrixes!
great matrix of underrated run double rainbow says it all.
